Description: is a Danish delicacy brand which has a great love for the French pantry, for "La vie francaise" and we offer a number of honest and authentic delicacies which are mainly produced in Provence. Often with a little delicate dispute, if we have fallen for a special composition that suits the taste. We offer everything from extra virgin olive oil, pasta, salt grinders to jams and chocolates - and much more. The goal is a sensuous experience, created to add spice to everyday meals and bring out more nuances in cooking. The many ingredients we use in our simple recipes come from our producers' fields in the South of France. We combine the pure quality with a stylish, Scandinavian expression and look that also tells the story of the good life and makes you want to have the products standing out in the home. All items are packed in sustainable packagings and can be recycled. Bon appetit!

Description: o us, the home is an honest reflection of who we are and what we stand for. We create our homes. And our homes create us. We all come with a fingerspitz gefühl for the Danish Design heritage, which has been passed down through generations. A combination of timeless and on-trend design expressions is what we are striving for, and last but not least: Happiness. When we talk about happiness, it’s about seeing beauty in the small things and enjoying both aesthetics and unique details. We carefully think out materials and colour choices around the feeling of happiness because we strongly believe happiness is of the essence. It permeates everything we do: from idea to finished product, and all the way to the end-user. Happiness is simply at the core of the Hübsch brand ethos.
